WEBVTT

1
01:15:07.750 --> 01:15:09.670 
今年不是一个人了
I'm not alone this year.

2
01:15:11.780 --> 01:15:12.900 
我往天上看
And I'm looking up now,

3
01:15:12.900 --> 01:15:15.030 
随着雪花缓缓飘落
as the snow comes drifting down,

4
01:15:15.080 --> 01:15:17.500 
一轮冬月发出淡淡微光
and I see a pale winter moon

5
01:15:17.600 --> 01:15:19.820 
映照时代广场
over Times Square...

6
01:15:20.250 --> 01:15:22.130 
新的一年
as the new year starts

7
01:15:22.610 --> 01:15:24.470 
也以缓缓的步伐
its lumbering journey

8
01:15:24.700 --> 01:15:26.080 
迈向永恒
into eternity...

